author: Squidmar Miniatures
description:
Come join the battle against in Warhammer 40.000: Tacticus, free to download. Enter code: SQUIDMAS for some in game treats! https://play.tacticusgame.com/squidmas

In this Video, I had the pleasure to paint with one of the worlds best painters, and Warhammer painting world champion Borja Calvo Bertran De Lis for a full 24h hours. You'll get to learn along side me and see two awesome armies shape up during the session!
